name: Pirate's Sloop
description_trait: This agile little vessel relies on its superior handling to evade attacks as it can’t take many hits.

name: Wood
description_trait: Wood is good for more than replacing a leg. It can be used to create Wooden Oars, and much much more...

name: Jug of Rum
description_trait: A jug of delicious rum. This will restore 5 Energy.

name: Cotton
description_trait: Soft, fluffy cotton. This is useful for crafting cool items like Cotton Nets.

name: Iron Ore
description_trait: Strong, heavy iron ore. This is useful for crafting items like Iron Anchors.

name: Town Hall
description_trait: Raise the flag over your Town Hall and let the Jolly Roger smile!

name: Bulletin Board
description_trait: Ahoy! Need for more gold, iron, loot and booty? Take a job, set sail, succeed and collect your rewards. Savvy?

name: Blacksmith
description_trait: Man the bellows and fire the forge! Visit the Smithy to Craft new items and upgrade old ones.

name: Gold Keg Statue
description_trait: A way to honor the container of a pirate's best friend. Very shiny.

name: Parrot Totem
description_trait: An emblem of a beautiful and intelligent creature. Looks stackable.

name: Small Rock
description_trait: A lump of earth. Modest in size.

name: Medium Rock
description_trait: A lump of earth. Average in size.

name: Palm Tree
description_trait: It's a tree mate. Good for shade.

name: Bush
description_trait: This be a shrub. That's all it be mate.

name: Wood Chest
description_trait: A treasure chest made out of wood. Kinda light and smells like a tree.

name: Founder's Iron Chest
description_trait: An Iron clad treasure chest. Heavy-ish she be.

name: Founder's Bronze Chest
description_trait: Bronzed be this treasure chest. Me heart grows heavier with delight of its weight.

name: Founder's Silver Chest
description_trait: Silver like the moon over the seas this beauty treasure chest be. Kinda heavy now says I.

name: Founder's Gold Chest
description_trait: A Golden Treasure Chest that glistens like the morning sun over the horizon. Definitely heavy with hopes of fine treasure.

name: Founder's Map Piece I
description_trait: Well lookey here me matey, a Founder’s Map with inklings of it leading to something special.

name: Founder's Map Piece II
description_trait: Well shiver me timbers! A Founder’s Map, it looks like it points to something a pirate would love.

name: Founder's Map Piece III
description_trait: A Founder’s Map just itching to tell us where it hides some juicy treasure.

name: Founder's Map Piece IV
description_trait: A Founder’s Map, let's unlock its secrets and its treasure location.

name: Mailbox
description_trait: A way to receive news that is personal to you.

name: Pirate Nation Flag
description_trait: Mark yer isle with yer colors and show all those scallywags that it be yer sand they be standing on.

name: Gold Pirate Statue
description_trait: A way to honor some scallywag. Very shiny.

name: Cherry Blossom Tree
description_trait: A tree that has beautiful pink flowers.

name: Large Rock
description_trait: A lump of earth. Kind of massive in size.

name: Fence
description_trait: Keeps out unwanted visitors.

name: Monkey Totem
description_trait: A totem of Bobo, the Monkey Pirate! Looks stackable.

name: Goldfish Totem
description_trait: A totem of a forgetful creature. Looks stackable.

name: Goblin Totem
description_trait: A totem of a mischievous creature. Looks stackable.

name: Topiary Pirate Statue
description_trait: A way to honor some scallywag. Well-trimmed.

name: Rogue's Galleon
description_trait: A rare galleon fit for pirate royalty.

name: Energy Coil
description_trait: Get a charge every day from this mecha-sparky-thing! Generates a Flask of Rum daily. NOTE: Only one Energy Coil is effective per Starter Island.

name: Triple Wind Mill
description_trait: Wind? Rum. Magic! Generates a Jug of Rum daily. NOTE: Only one Triple Wind Mill is effective per Starter Island.

name: Hammock
description_trait: Take a proper snooze at bedtime or lollygag the day away you lazy scurvy dog.

name: Pirate Archway
description_trait: A curved entrance. Pirate-y in nature.

name: Tiki Head Statue
description_trait: A statue of a tiki head.

name: Tiki Bar
description_trait: A must-have for a pirate party.

name: Inflatable Pirate
description_trait: Why I've never seen a finer representation of a Pirate full of hot air.

name: Barrrbecue
description_trait: A must-have when celebrating on yer Island with yer mateys!

name: Marketplace
description_trait: Buy and sell value goods here.

name: Bank
description_trait: A place to manage yer booty!

name: Stone Pathway
description_trait: A pathway made of stone.

name: Compass
description_trait: Find yer way with this handy little do-dad.

name: Spyglass
description_trait: This helps ye see what's on the horizon.

name: Mermaid Scale
description_trait: Mermaids will shed these pretty scales on rare occasions.

name: Wooden Oar
description_trait: Wooden Oars be used to move yer ship through the shallows and when the wind dies down.

name: Iron Anchor
description_trait: Anchors will hold yer ship still in the storm matey.

name: Cotton Net
description_trait: Nets be used to haul things up from the deep.

name: Flask of Rum
description_trait: A flask of delicious rum. This will restore 2 Energy.

name: Keg of Rum
description_trait: A keg of delicious rum. This will restore 25 Energy.

name: Kelp
description_trait: The grass of the sea, only longer...and slimy.

name: Coral Reef
description_trait: Home to many beautiful fish.

name: Skeleton in the Sand
description_trait: That poor mate drank his last jug. Not the worst way to go.

name: Pirate's Galleon
description_trait: This mid-sized, stout ship is the heart of any fleet.

name: Pirate's Skiff
description_trait: The Skiff lacks in most areas, but it's seaworthy.

name: Pirate's Frigate
description_trait: This ship is the heart of any fleet and a real powerhouse on the open seas.

name: Pirate's Marauder
description_trait: This ship is the elite war ship and a battle master of the open seas.

name: Iron Cannonball
description_trait: A ball of iron that goes in a cannon…appropriately named don't you think?

name: Iron Cannon
description_trait: Ignite the fuse to make holes in your target. Affix to a ship to add Heavy Blow to its deck. Only one card of each type may be added this way.

name: Wooden Helm
description_trait: This here wheel turns, and the boats follows. Affix to a ship to add Careful Planning to its deck. Only one card of each type may be added this way.

name: Faded Map
description_trait: This faded old map looks like it might lead to a treasure of some kind!

name: Puzzle Totem
description_trait: Avast! This totem represents that you are a Pirate Nation puzzle winner! U R Smart.

name: Cannon Fuse
description_trait: This is an explosively important part that is used in the crafting of a cannon.

name: Wooden Column
description_trait: This holds the ship's helm. That's the wheel thingy for you landlubbers out there.

name: Hemp Rope
description_trait: Ropes are to a ship's sails as a belt is to a pirates pants.

name: Iron Rivets
description_trait: These are used to hold the reinforced hull plates to the ship.

name: Worn Copper Coin
description_trait: An ancient, worn copper coin from a forgotten era.

name: Glimmering Silver Coin
description_trait: A well-worn silver piece that appears to be hundreds of years old. It still glimmers when polished.

name: Ancient Gold Coin
description_trait: A tarnished gold coin from a fallen civilization. It radiates with an aura of power.

name: Iron Needle
description_trait: This is the pointy thingy in a sight that marks the target that is about to get hit by a heavy round thingy.

name: High Seas Map
description_trait: This pretty map promises adventures on the high seas.

name: Cutlass
description_trait: Cutlass. No sir. I say cut more!

name: Billy Club
description_trait: It's always good to have Billy around, just in case.

name: Iron Armor
description_trait: These plates will provide some protection from those cannons. Affix to a ship to add Hardened Shield to its deck. Only one card of each type may be added this way.

name: Plans: Sloop I
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Sloop.

name: Plans: Sloop II
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Sloop.

name: Plans: Sloop III
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Sloop.

name: Plans: Sloop IV
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Sloop.

name: Plans: Galleon I
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Galleon.

name: Plans: Galleon II
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Galleon.

name: Plans: Galleon III
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Galleon.

name: Plans: Galleon IV
description_trait: Collect all 4 plans to create Completed Plans: Galleon.

name: Iron Sights
description_trait: Cannons can be a bit inaccurate, but these Sights will help them hit their target. Affix to a ship to add Hit the Dry Powder to its deck. Only one card of each type may be added this way.

name: Fish Food
description_trait: This shaker contains fish food. Seems harmless.

name: Crate of Bananas
description_trait: A simple crate of bananas. Right?

name: Grappling Hook
description_trait: This little thing allows you to reach new heights.

name: Dagger
description_trait: Nothing helps get your point across when negotiating like a dagger.

name: Musket
description_trait: A pirate's best friend.

name: Cotton Sail
description_trait: These sails will give your ship some zip! Affix to a ship to add Act with Haste to its deck. Only one card of each type may be added this way.

name: Docks
description_trait: Sittin' on the Dock of the Bay…

name: Plans: Skiff I
description_trait: Collect both plans to create Completed Plans: Skiff

name: Plans: Skiff II
description_trait: Collect both plans to create Completed Plans: Skiff

name: Completed Plan: Skiff
description_trait: This is a completed Plan for a Skiff class pirate ship.

name: Completed Plan: Sloop
description_trait: This is a completed Plan for a Sloop class pirate ship.

name: Completed Plan: Galleon
description_trait: This is a completed Plan for a Galleon class pirate ship.

name: Founder's Whoopsie Chest
description_trait: Odd looking chest that seems to be of unknown origin. There are words inscribed on the side: 'devs do something!'

name: Trivia Totem
description_trait: A curious totem for know-it-alls.
